    {
      "type": "text", "id": "wiki_text", "x": 720, "y": 105, "width": 260, "height": 265,
      "text": "wiki/ (Layer 2)\n\nindex.md — retrieval catalog\nlog.md — operation history\n\nEntities (people, tools, companies)\nConcepts & Patterns\n  · Harness Engineering\n  · System Design\n  · Developer Experience\nSynthesis (query file-backs)\nConnections (first-class)\nVisuals (.excalidraw)\nSource summaries\n\n───────────────────\nCLAUDE.md (Layer 3)\nSchema + commands + skills",
      "originalText": "wiki/ (Layer 2)\n\nindex.md — retrieval catalog\nlog.md — operation history\n\nEntities (people, tools, companies)\nConcepts & Patterns\n  · Harness Engineering\n  · System Design\n  · Developer Experience\nSynthesis (query file-backs)\nConnections (first-class)\nVisuals (.excalidraw)\nSource summaries\n\n───────────────────\nCLAUDE.md (Layer 3)\nSchema + commands + skills",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
